oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o1uQ148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fo1uQ148.jpg&h=3dbc24ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n庭鋒仲喺英國讀過高中<br />\n喺當地大學讀PE<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7XGSR5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7XGSR5x.jpg&h=04c05977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(張相著背心真係犯哂規啦)<br />\n返嚟一口流利英文<br />\n做埋明珠台節目添<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靚仔過哂所有主持添<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/e2qSEIK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fe2qSEIK.jpg&h=d5ba8715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/66LDCH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F66LDCH5.jpg&h=e09d02c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nJNuj57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnJNuj57.jpg&h=21df13b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n庭鋒仲係踢波出身<br />\n運動健獎又sporty<br />\n冧死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fULdFIS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfULdFIS.jpg&h=15e58620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n著起校服仲制服誘惑人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cjFinNv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcjFinNv.jpg&h=199137ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮學生少年冇違和感<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.i